{"title":"demographics_help","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"markdown":"This panel shows **the history of contributors active in last 10 years** focused on the first and last contribution of each person.

**WARNING**: Pre-computed data displayed. Dynamic filters like time picker won't work as expected.

* If clicking on `Attracted Developers` you will get a view based on them that allows you to know where they made their last contribution.
* If clicking on `People Leaving` you will get a view based on them that allows you to know where they were attracted to the community.
